Package banana.positionallist

Class LinkedPositionalList<E>

java.lang.Object
banana.positionallist.LinkedPositionalList<E>
Type Parameters:
E - type of elements that will be stored in Positions of this list.
All Implemented Interfaces:
PositionalList<E>
public class LinkedPositionalList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements PositionalList<E>
Concrete implementation of a PositionalList using a doubly linked list.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Gilbert Ssenyonjo

    Produces the Position immediately after Position p or null if p is the last Position in the list.
    Position<E> before​(Position<E> p)
    Produces the Position immediately before Position p or null if p is the first Position in the list.
